data.name: AC接口转发速率趋势
data.categoryName: AC性能分析/AC接口转发流量趋势

data.customSql:
select hour,ac_base_mac,day,weekstart,weekend,month,year,datatype,
ac_ip,ac_if_type,ac_if_mac,ac_if_ipv4,ac_if_index,ac_if_name,
avgifrxrate,
maxifrxrate,
minifrxrate,
avgiftxrate,
maxiftxrate,
miniftxrate,
round(CAST(CAST(avgifrxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) avgifrxrate_kbps,
round(CAST(CAST(maxifrxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) maxifrxrate_kbps,
round(CAST(CAST(minifrxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) minifrxrate_kbps,
round(CAST(CAST(avgiftxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) avgiftxrate_kbps,
round(CAST(CAST(maxiftxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) maxiftxrate_kbps,
round(CAST(CAST(miniftxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) miniftxrate_kbps,
round(CAST(CAST(avgifrxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024*1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) avgifrxrate_mbps,
round(CAST(CAST(maxifrxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024*1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) maxifrxrate_mbps,
round(CAST(CAST(minifrxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024*1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) minifrxrate_mbps,
round(CAST(CAST(avgiftxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024*1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) avgiftxrate_mbps,
round(CAST(CAST(maxiftxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024*1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) maxiftxrate_mbps,
round(CAST(CAST(miniftxrate as DECIMAL)/(1024*1024) as DECIMAL ), 3) miniftxrate_mbps
from ac_int_traffic_rate_trend where datatype IN (1)  and 1=1
and ac_if_mac in (select ac_if_mac from (select ac_if_mac,count(*)cnt from ac_int_traffic_rate_trend where 1=1 and datatype in(1) and avgifrxrate>0 group by ac_if_mac order by count(*)  desc limit 1)tb1)

data.name: 新增AC数
data.categoryName: 资源统计/AC设备数量统计

data.customSql:
SELECT userid,hour,day,weekstart,weekend,month,year,datatype,acnumfirst,acnumlast,(acnumlast-acnumfirst) growthacnum
FROM 
  (SELECT userid,hour,day,weekstart,weekend,month,year,datatype,acnum acnumfirst
	  FROM ac_statistic 
	  WHERE 1=1
	  ORDER BY hour ASC
    LIMIT 1) cb_view_first,
  (SELECT acnum acnumlast
	  FROM ac_statistic 
	  WHERE 1=1
	  ORDER BY hour DESC
    LIMIT 1) cb_view_last

data.customSql:
SELECT userid,hour,day,weekstart,weekend,month,year,datatype,(apenablenumlast - apenablenumfirst) growthapnum
 FROM
 (SELECT userid,hour,day,weekstart,weekend,month,year,datatype, 
           apenablenum,apdisablenum,apnum,growthapnum,circular_growth_ratio,apenablenum apenablenumfirst
  FROM ap_statistic WHERE 1=1
  ORDER BY hour ASC
  LIMIT 1) cb_view_first,
 (SELECT apenablenum apenablenumlast 
  FROM ap_statistic 
  WHERE 1=1
  ORDER BY hour DESC 
  LIMIT 1) cb_view_last

data.name: 区域数量
data.categoryName: 资源统计/区域数量统计

data.customSql:
SELECT arealevelfirst AS arealevel, userid, 
       hour, day, weekstart, weekend, month, year, datatype, areanumfirst AS areanum, (areanumlast - areanumfirst) AS growthareanum
	FROM 
	 (SELECT concat(arealevel,'级区域') as arealevelfirst, MIN(userid) AS userid, 
		 MIN(hour) AS hour, MIN(day) AS day, MIN(weekstart) AS weekstart, MIN(weekend) AS weekend, 
		 MIN(month) AS month, MIN(year) AS year, MIN(datatype) AS datatype,SUM(areanum) areanumfirst
		 FROM  area_statistic 
		 WHERE 1=1
		 AND hour = (SELECT MIN(hour) FROM area_statistic WHERE 1=1)
		 GROUP BY arealevel
		 ORDER BY arealevel ASC)cb_view_first,
	 (SELECT concat(arealevel,'级区域') as arealevellast, MAX(userid) useridlast, 
		 SUM(areanum) areanumlast
		 FROM  area_statistic 
		 WHERE 1=1
		 AND hour = (SELECT MAX(hour) FROM area_statistic WHERE 1=1)
		 GROUP BY arealevel)cb_view_last
	WHERE arealevelfirst=arealevellast
